#. Plugin Name of the plugin
msgid "WooCommerce Cart Recovery"
msgstr "WooCommerce Cart Recovery"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
msgid "https://example.com/plugins/woocommerce-cart-recovery"
msgstr ""

#. Description of the plugin
msgid "Recover abandoned WooCommerce carts and pending orders with scheduled reminders, native coupons and locale-aware emails."
msgstr "Stellt abgebrochene WooCommerce-Warenkörbe und ausstehende Bestellungen mit geplanten Erinnerungen, nativen Gutscheinen und sprachabhängigen E-Mails wieder her."

#. Author of the plugin
msgid "22MW"
msgstr ""

